A4.text: Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart was born and raised in Salzburg.

A5.text: Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart was born on 27 January 1756 at Getreidegasse 9 in Salzburg.

A6.text: He was baptised the day after his birth, at St. Rupert's Cathedral in Salzburg.
